        {
            "+content": "Forty-year-old detective Eiji Kirisame has found maybe the strangest witness of his life: a silent high school girl named Tsugumi Kuchinashi who was at the scene of the crime. Her statements mostly consist of shoddy doodles on a drawing pad, but Eiji is no stranger to piecing together the truth from limited evidence―and besides, it seems like Tsugumi might have a knack for deduction. So he'll take every page seriously if it might help solve the case. <em class=de-emphasized>(from manga)</em>",
